lines.text: as we march side by side
and the tales from the old
hear the cries as they fall
with the power of the sword
pray for the master of war
sunlight will fall by the wastelands
endless rise for the heroes before
reckoning day for the demons we slay
with the force of a dragon
nightmares return of the thousand screaming
rise for the heroes once more
in the eyes of broken dreams
outside of the wasted and torn
a land of tears still remains
and the fallen will rise up again
blessed by the union of man

paragraphs.text: time after time as we march side by side through the valleys of evil and the torturing souls night after night for the glory we fight in the kingdom of madness and the tales from the old

march on through the hellfire blazing from the darkness beyond nightmares return of the thousand screaming rise for the heroes once more
